{"tid":1797432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕反思] 比人話cool/kam點改善","createTime":"2019-12-25T12:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T14:59:49.000Z","uid":322974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75fd39ef98502b07992cfb69a2c8d066b4557559","tid":1797432,"uid":322974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"老豆食軟飯 會郁手 深藍 怨天尤人 又鍾意點人做野<br />\n所以鍾意將d野收收埋埋 唔想同屋企人講咁多<br />\n但發覺份人好cool 整到個人好毒咁<br />\n雖然已經睇好多戲/好笑野平衡下 <br />\n同人傾謁都引到人笑<br />\n但成日要人地做主動好唔健康<br />\n想知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMerry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2ed66388bf149fb6cffcd062748bd88f7c0b21","tid":1797432,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"What is kam"},{"pid":"bf85f67de58b607e67b9c19165cc2853cfc99469","tid":1797432,"uid":322974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2ed66388bf149fb6cffcd062748bd88f7c0b21","tid":1797432,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"What is kam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"應該係奇怪"},{"pid":"587544dda0cb41a1a20a45b8fbd9b16ed2f325b7","tid":1797432,"uid":10786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf85f67de58b607e67b9c19165cc2853cfc99469","tid":1797432,"uid":322974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2ed66388bf149fb6cffcd062748bd88f7c0b21","tid":1797432,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"What is kam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"應該係奇怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"唔係gay咩"},{"pid":"dbd5d4177eaf8b22a31fda6f95fdd03c89903684","tid":1797432,"uid":322974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587544dda0cb41a1a20a45b8fbd9b16ed2f325b7","t